{"name": "integry", "metadata": {"name": "integry", "version": "0.0.1", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "The official Python library for the Integry API", "upload_time": 1734045360}, "documentation": ["# Integry Python API Library\n\nThe Python API library allows access to Integry REST API from Python programs.\n\n# Installation\n\n```bash\n# install from PyPI\npip install integry\n```\n\n# Usage\n\n```python\nimport os\nfrom integry import Integry\n\nuser_id = \"your user's ID\"\n\n# Initialize the client\nintegry = Integry(\n    app_secret=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_KEY\"),\n    app_key=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_SECRET\"),\n)\n\n# Get the most relevant function\npredictions = await integry.functions.predict(prompt=\"say hello to my team on Slack\", user_id=user_id, predict_arguments=True)\n\nif predictions:\n    function = predictions[0]\n    # Call the function\n    await function(user_id, function.arguments)\n```\n\n# Pagination\nList methods are paginated and allow you to iterate over data without handling pagination manually.\n```python\nfrom integry import Integry\n\nuser_id = \"your user's ID\"\n\nintegry = Integry(\n    app_secret=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_KEY\"),\n    app_key=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_SECRET\"),\n)\n\nasync for function in integry.functions.list(user_id):\n    # do something with function\n    print(function.name)\n```\n\nIf you want to control pagination, you can fetch individual pages by using the `cursor` returned by the previous page.\n```python\nfrom integry import Integry\n\nuser_id = \"your user's ID\"\n\nintegry = Integry(\n    app_secret=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_KEY\"),\n    app_key=os.environ.get(\"INTEGRY_APP_SECRET\"),\n)\n\nfirst_page = await integry.apps.list(user_id)\n\nsecond_page = await integry.apps.list(user_id, cursor=first_page.cursor)\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "integry.resources.apps.api", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "integry.resources.apps.api.Apps", "bases": ["BaseResource"], "methods": [{"name": "integry.resources.apps.api.Apps.list", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "cursor", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "AsyncPaginator", "xref": {"fqname": "integry.resources.base.AsyncPaginator", "project": null}, "params": [{"name": "App", "xref": {"fqname": "integry.resources.apps.api.types.App", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "AppsPage", "xref": {"fqname": "integry.resources.apps.api.types.AppsPage", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "integry.resources.apps.api.Apps.get", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "integry.resources.apps.api.Apps.is_connected", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "app_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "user_id", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params"